#: includes/class-lrob-calendar-admin.php:308
msgid ""
"When disabled, events and their taxonomies are only accessible through the "
"calendar. Direct URLs return 404, and frontend links are stripped from "
"blocks and the calendar popup."
msgstr ""
"Si désactivé, les événements et leurs taxonomies ne sont accessibles que via "
"le calendrier. L'accès direct aux URL renvoie une erreur 404, et les liens "
"sont retirés des blocs et de l'infobulle du calendrier."

#: includes/class-lrob-calendar-admin.php:314
msgid "Maximum event age"
msgstr "Ancienneté maximale des événements"

#: includes/class-lrob-calendar-admin.php:319
msgid "months"
msgstr "mois"

#: includes/class-lrob-calendar-admin.php:321
msgid ""
"Queries that don't set their own date range will ignore events older than "
"this. Use 0 for no limit. Helps performance on sites with thousands of "
"historical events."
msgstr ""
"Les requêtes qui ne fixent pas leur propre plage de dates ignoreront les "
"événements plus anciens. Utilisez 0 pour ne pas limiter. Améliore les "
"performances sur les sites comportant des milliers d'événements historiques."

#: includes/class-lrob-calendar-admin.php:327
